Requirements:
1.	The game MUST have a single blue cycle and three enemy yellow cycles
2.  The player MUST be able to only turn left and right
3.  The player cycle MUST have a line behind it that can destroy enemy cycles
4.  The player MUST lose if they touch a yellow cycle line
5.	The game MUST run at a slowly increasing speed, starting from very slow
6.	The game MUST include a countdown clock starting from 3 minutes
7.	The game MUST have a score that increases with each enemy takedown
8.	The game MUST be cross compatible with Windows/Linux/MacOS
9.	The game MAY be cross compatible with x86/Arm
10.	The game MUST have a black background
11.	The game MUST be simple and user-friendly
12.	The game MAY have multiplayer capabilities
13.	The game MUST be tested and approved by game testers
